---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const bgStyle = 'background-image: url("/images/hero1.jpg")';
---

<Layout title="AC Kings of Arizona">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero  -->
    <section
      class="home-hero relative bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
      style={bgStyle}>
      <div
        class="relative mx-auto max-w-screen-xl py-10 px-8 lg:py-32 lg:flex lg:items-center">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-800">
            YOUR TRUSTED AC HOME SERVICE IN THE <strong class="text-indigo-800"
              >VALLEY</strong
            >
          </h1>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-center">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="block w-full rounded bg-orange-600 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow hover:bg-orange-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring sm:w-auto">
              Schedule Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <!-- Royalty is in our DNA -->
      <div class="bg-white py-16">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl lg:text-center">
            <h2
              class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
              Royalty is in our DNA
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
              We understand that to a homeowner, their home is their palace.
              Repairing and maintaining your home can be quite the hassle.
              Because this is a common belief, we make sure that homeowners in
              need of tune ups, repairs, and installations of new HVAC units get
              the Royal treatment here at AC Kings.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-20 lg:max-w-5xl">
            <div
              class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
              <div class="relative md:pl-16">
                <div
                  class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 mb-4">
                  <h3>Our Technicians are trained to</h3>
                </div>
                <ul role="list" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-gray-600">
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Treat you, your time, and your home with respect
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Actively listen to understand your problems
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Present the best possible options
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Agree on price before work starts
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Perform work efficiently and promptly
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="relative md:pl-16">
                <div
                  class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 mb-4">
                  <h3>Every Technician is</h3>
                </div>
                <ul role="list" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-gray-600">
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Licensed and certified
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Drug tested
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Competent and efficient
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Willing and ready to comply with safety codes
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg
                      class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
                      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      aria-hidden="true">
                      <path
                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Take pride in their work
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ready to earn your business -->
      <div class="mt-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-600 to-indigo-700 py-16">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-10 text-white text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
            We are ready to earn your trust and business
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl font-light text-slate-100 leading-8">
            We know that there are lots of options to choose from when finding a
            company that will fit all of your needs. We hope to instill trust in
            you and the community so when you call us, you are certain you will
            be taken care of. Our goal in this industry is to provide the least
            number of headaches, while accomplishing your goals to upgrade your
            home. All in all, to provide the best service around. We will walk
            you through our process and never push you into a decision. We will
            however make sure that we understand your concerns and preferences
            very clearly so that you and heard and taken care of.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <p class="mb-8 text-xl">
              If you have questions please call so we can roll out the red
              carpet for you.
            </p>
            <a
              href="tel:4806007340"
              class="rounded bg-orange-600 px-4 py-2 text-md font-medium text-white shadow hover:bg-orange-500">
              Call Today (480) 600-7340
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services offered -->
      <div class="py-16">
        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Keeping you Cool with our Royal Services
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600">
            Simple & Predictable pricing. No Suprises.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl mt-14 px-12">
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-col w-full border-2 border-slate-300 border-opacity-50 py-14 px-8 rounded-md">
              <div class="flex justify-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600">
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M12 6.75a5.25 5.25 0 016.775-5.025.75.75 0 01.313 1.248l-3.32 3.319c.063.475.276.934.641 1.299.365.365.824.578 1.3.64l3.318-3.319a.75.75 0 011.248.313 5.25 5.25 0 01-5.472 6.756c-1.018-.086-1.87.1-2.309.634L7.344 21.3A3.298 3.298 0 112.7 16.657l8.684-7.151c.533-.44.72-1.291.634-2.309A5.342 5.342 0 0112 6.75zM4.117 19.125a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h.008a.75.75 0 01.75.75v.008a.75.75 0 01-.75.75h-.008a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75v-.008z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center my-4">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold">Tune Ups</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4">
                Our tune ups team doesn’t only check your ac, they are trained
                to make sure that your entire system is performing at peak
                condition. From the filters to the individual components of your
                equipment, everything is tested to manufactured code. Call to
                get a certified tech sent to you.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-col w-full border-2 border-slate-300 border-opacity-50 py-14 px-8 rounded-md">
              <div class="flex justify-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600">
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25zM12.75 6a.75.75 0 00-1.5 0v6c0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-3.75V6z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center my-4">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold">Repairs</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4">
                Whether your air conditioner is underperforming, or not working
                at all, in most cases it usually can be repaired. Our certified
                technicians will diagnose the problem, present the options and
                agree on price before before any work will be done. Do you need
                any repairs done?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex flex-col w-full border-2 border-slate-300 border-opacity-50 py-14 px-8 rounded-md">
              <div class="flex justify-center">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600">
                  <path
                    d="M11.47 3.84a.75.75 0 011.06 0l8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06l-8.689-8.69a2.25 2.25 0 00-3.182 0l-8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 001.061 1.06l8.69-8.69z"
                  ></path>
                  <path
                    d="M12 5.432l8.159 8.159c.03.03.06.058.091.086v6.198c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H15a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75v-4.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-3a.75.75 0 00-.75.75V21a.75.75 0 01-.75.75H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 01-1.875-1.875v-6.198a2.29 2.29 0 00.091-.086L12 5.43z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center my-4">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold">Installations</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4">
                When repairs can’t be done, or the damage is too extensive, it’s
                time to replace the system. One of our HVAC experts will come
                and see what options are available and present them to you. As
                before we will not push a decision on you and both parties will
                agree on a price before any work is done.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
